---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import Puzzles from '@components/ellenora/Puzzles';
---

<Layout title="Happy Birthday My pretty baby">
    <section class="box pt-24 pb-32">
        <h1 class="galada text-4xl text-center rainbow-letters uppercase">Happy Birthday, Mi ni√±a bonita!!</h1>
    </section>
	<section class="max-w-[650px] mx-auto">
        <p class="pb-4">Every moment with you feels like a gift, and today, I want to celebrate you for the incredible person you are. Your strength inspires me, your smile lights up my world, and your love fills my heart with joy.</p>
        <p class="pb-4">On this special day, I want you to know how much you mean to me. No matter the distance, my love for you only grows stronger. You are my light, my muse, and my greatest treasure.</p>
        <p class="pb-4">May this birthday bring you as much happiness as you bring into my life. Here's to you, to us, and to many more beautiful moments together.</p>
        <p>With all my love,</p>
        <p>Leo</p>
    </section>
    <section class="pt-32">
        <p class="text-center animate-bounce"><i class="nf nf-md-arrow_down"></i></p>
    </section>
    <section class="pt-16 pb-28 max-w-[650px] mx-auto">
        <p class="text-center text-slate-400">To make this more fun, I have prepared a couple of mini-games with simple puzzles, I hope you like them as much as I did when programming them.</p>
        <div class="py-32 min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
            <!-- <PuzzlesContainer client:load /> -->
             <Puzzles client:load />
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
<style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Galada&display=swap');
    .galada {
        font-family: "Galada", serif;
        font-weight: 400;
        font-style: normal;
    }

    p { 
        font-size: 1.45rem;
        line-height: 2rem;
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    }

    .rainbow-letters {
        margin-top: 0px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #ef5350, #f48fb1, #7e57c2, #2196f3, #26c6da, #43a047, #eeff41, #f9a825, #ff5722);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-size: content;
    }
</style>